Interface VolumeSnapshotBuilder

public interface VolumeSnapshotBuilder
extends Buildable.Builder<VolumeSnapshotBuilder,VolumeSnapshot>

A Builder which creates a Volume Snapshot. NOTE: The only REQUIRED field when creating a snapshot is volume(String) . All other fields are optional
